             <div class="view view-welcome view-id-welcome view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-9"> 
              <div class="view-content"> 
               <h2 class="block-title">Welcome Note</h2> 
               <div class="title_sep"></div> 
               <p>Bangladesh Islami University (BIU) was established in 2005 by the trust of this University with a mission to establish this university as an ideal institute of higher education and research in the private sector of Bangladesh. The Trust is a non-political and non-profit voluntary organization, registered with the Government of the People's Republic of Bangladesh.</p>
