        <h2 class="block-title">News Flash <a href="/news_flash"> <img src="/sites/all/themes/simply_modern/images/rssf.gif"></a> </h2> 
        <div class="title_sep"></div> 
        <div class="content">
         <div class="view view-news-flash-block view-id-news_flash_block view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-8"> 
          <div class="view-content"> 
           <div style="padding-bottom:5px;">
            <a href="/content/visit-ambassador-saudi-arabia-biu">Visit by the Ambassador of Saudi Arabia at BIU</a> 
            <br> 
            <p style="text-align: justify;">Bangladesh Islamic University (BIU) was visited by the Honorable Ambassador of Saudi Arabia and Honorable Chief Patron of BIU Dr. Abdullah Naser Al-Busiary. A meeting was held at the conference room of BIU on behalf of their visit. Founder, Board of Trusties of the university Professor Kamaluddin Abdullah Jafri welcomed them with Crest and Address of Honor. The Ambassador said he is happy to see the progress of BIU in such a short time. He also said Saudi Government will help BIU at every development of it. Deputy Head of Mission, Saudi Embassy, Mr.</p> 
            <p style="padding:0px;text-align:right;"> <span class="date-display-single">10/17/2011</span> </p> 
            <div style="text-align:right;padding-top:10px;"> 
             <a href="/content/visit-ambassador-saudi-arabia-biu">Read More</a> 
